text: Julian Bradley (born 16 July 1992) is an Irish tennis player. Bradley has a career high ATP singles ranking of 1325 achieved on 3 December 2018. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 483 achieved on 3 December 2018. Bradley represents Ireland at the Davis Cup, where he has a W/L record of 2–0.
